# NEMETIC STRING
# Alan_Watts_Interdependence (C17A)

Φ(Alan_Watts_Interdependence) = σ(ceramic|automatic) ∘ ρ(separation|interdependence) ∘ λ(alienation|integration) ∘ β(entity|field) ∘ δγ(self|universe) ∘ μ(model|experience) + ε | :interconnected_awareness

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(ceramic|automatic)            :: Air  :: Tension between ceramic and fully automatic models of reality
# ρ(separation|interdependence)   :: Water :: Flow between separation and interdependence
# λ(alienation|integration)       :: Fire  :: Transformation from alienation to holistic integration
# β(entity|field)                 :: Wood  :: Organic relationship between entity and field
# δγ(self|universe)               :: Earth :: Grounding of self within the universe
# μ(model|experience)             :: Metal :: Structure of models giving way to direct experience
